- ref: 
http://www.craigkerstiens.com/2013/02/21/more-out-of-psql/
http://merlinmoncure.blogspot.com/2007/10/better-psql-with-less.html

- config: .psqlrc

- configuring the pager in .psqlrc

    \timing
    \pset pager always
    \setenv LESS '-iMSx4 -FX'

- send output to a file

    > \o /tmp/psql-session

    - you can then optionally follow the file with less

    $ less /tmp/psql-session
